OL,3,CWhy are MPs debating an emergency bill
OL,4,Cto save British Steel?
OL,6,F"It doesn't mean all options are on
OL,7,Fthe table, but it means all options
OL,8,Fremain viable," he added.
OL,10,FIt comes as Jingye plans to close the
OL,11,Fblast furnaces and switch to a greener
OL,12,Fform of production.
OL,14,FThe steelworks in Sculthorpe currently
OL,15,Femploys 2,700 people.
OL,17,FThey claim the plant's two blast
OL,18,Ffurnaces are no longer financially
OL,19,Fsustainable and the raw materials
OL,20,Fneeded to keep them operational are
OL,21,Frunning out.
