OL,3,CWhy are MPs debating an emergency bill
OL,4,Cto save British Steel?
OL,6,FJingye said the business is running at
OL,7,Fa loss of #700,000 a day maintaining
OL,8,Fthe plant.
OL,10,FNumber 10 said they have been
OL,11,Fnegotiating with owners ever since
OL,12,Fcoming to office, reassuring them that
OL,13,Fthere is a bright future for steel in
OL,14,Fthe UK.
OL,16,FThe government has been urged to
OL,17,Fnationalise the business as union
OL,18,Fbosses said the future of the
OL,19,FScunthorpe steelworks is "on a knife-
OL,20,Fedge".
