OL,3,CWhy are MPs debating an emergency bill
OL,4,Cto save British Steel?
OL,6,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch said the
OL,7,Fproblem should have been resolved
OL,8,Fmonths ago and warned that a large
OL,9,Fcost to taxpayers was "inevitable".
OL,11,F"The Labour government have landed
OL,12,Fthemselves in a steel crisis entirely
OL,13,Fof their own making. They've made poor
OL,14,Fdecisions and let the unions dictate
OL,15,Ftheir actions," she said.
